            "title": "財經｜恒生率先推全程數碼審批八成信貸擔保產品",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜恒生率先推全程數碼審批八成信貸擔保產品\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜恒生率先推全程數碼審批八成信貸擔保產品</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒生銀行指出，為政府「中小企融資擔保計劃」的八成信貸擔保產品，率先推全程數碼申請及批核、以電子身份驗證和電子簽署貸款文件，為首間推出有關服務的香港銀行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中小企客戶由網上申請該項貸款及提交文件，最快可在10秒內獲悉原則性批核結果，貸款額最高為800萬元。此外，透過與電子支付平台KPay及餐飲業點餐平台DimOrder合作，讓客戶可選擇使用替代數據，簡化無抵押中小企及貸款的申請。包括零售和餐飲業在內的中小企客戶，可減省提交銀行月結單，節省時間並加快審批流程，貸款上限將增1倍至400萬元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2726aeea-6801-3233-99ee-c21d4e9093cd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒生商業銀行業務總監李秀怡指出，服務將加快融資申請和效率；而為中小企提供替代數據選項，則有助減省傳統貸款繁瑣手續。優化措施將惠及額外5萬名合資格中小企客戶。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
